{"title":"我曾去过沙漠","date":"2018-04-14T10:19:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年4月14日","L":"2018/04/14","MM-DD":"04-14"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/12/fcs3X8Dad7NjUEK.jpg","link":"2018/04/14/我曾去过沙漠","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-01-09T17:48:13.814Z","content":"<blockquote><p>先是缓缓下滑\n然后快速坠落\n埋入沙中</p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<p>我曾去过沙漠\n细沙在风中塑舞\n连续的曲线\n像是女人的胴体\n光滑细索</p>\n<p>但我绝不敢停驻\n——先是缓缓下滑\n然后快速坠落\n埋入沙中</p>\n<p>醒来的是绿洲初曦的露珠\n还是随风而去的蜃楼\n都只是黄粱一梦</p>\n","prev":{"title":"只为再见到你","link":"2018/04/16/只为再见到你"},"next":{"title":"我们都曾沉沦于孤独","link":"2018/01/27/我们都曾沉沦于孤独"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/14/我曾去过沙漠/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","link":"<a href=\"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/14/我曾去过沙漠/\" title=\"我曾去过沙漠\">http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/14/我曾去过沙漠/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}